    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i guess i'm wondering about the \"opponents\" part though. some of the parents in the PTA group chat are saying this is basically indoctrination and that the school is overstepping. i'm trying to figure out if those concerns are actually based on something legitimate or if they're just being reactionary. how would you characterize the validity of those parental concerns compared to the school's reasoning?",
